&lt;p&gt;The Development hereby permitted shall only be carried out and completed strictly in accordance with the submitted plans hereby approved and any subsequent approval of details. This includes the planting areas in the front garden, which will screen the fire stairs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the development hereby permitted is carried out in full accordance with the plans hereby approved.
